PLUGIN.DESCRIPTION:
Oolong is an assembler like language for the Java
Virtual Machine. This plugin provides tools to:-

* Decompile class files to Oolong;
* Compile Oolong files to Java class files;
* Dump information about Java class files;
* Produce hex dumps of any file.

Oolong.xml is a mode file which may be installed in
jEdit to highlight Oolong files (see jEdit
